2-Internal distance only from the top and bottom
<div class="py-4 bg-gray-300">
text
</div>

note:
m-{number} → margin 
p-{number} → padding 

mt-, mb-, ml-, mr- → margin top/bottom/left/right
pt-, pb-, pl-, pr- → padding top/bottom/left/right
